{"tid":1659013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（新聞）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化","createTime":"2019-10-16T17:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:04:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9c321e49b0cc9d56bb9c1eb0031100210b149a8e","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:32:22.000Z","msg":"（新聞）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家都相知 近排唔只出面的和理非同勇武開始出現分化 依排係連登的手足都開始互相有分化現象出現<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得好奇怪 明明由運動到依家 連登的手足都係比較難分化的一群 點解依家會無故出現分現象<br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武都有現象想奪取運動的主流方向 係兄弟爬山 各自努力下 照計應該唔會出現依個問題<br />\n<br />\n我mon post都有一段可長的時間 發現依排多佐好撚多 所謂 - [長文] 去批評運動的方向 勇武同和理非都有 而且用字反映出來的語氣都係有責備的性質<br />\n<br />\n而依類所謂 長文 都不斷用 責備的形式同雙方最激的方法 製做和理非做法手足 同 勇武手足 的強烈反感/二元對立<br />\n導致引起反感的手足都出 所謂 長文 變相幫手助長依類風氣<br />\n<br />\n例如 :<br />\n綜合類<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣做就會導致運動失敗 最後責任就係你地 勇武/和理非<br />\n你屌你地全部老母<br />\n你地係唔係想搞死個運動<br />\n你地有無用腦架<br />\n<br />\nPS 依一類係用好嚴苛的 [blue]老師教同學 老母教仔 老手教新手 語氣 去責怪唔同立場意見的手足<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n三毛勇武類<br />\n<br />\n你地2014重味左輸夠 和理非有用就一早成功啦 和理非收返埋啦<br />\n我地應該進行無底線抗爭 (唔合理情況下)<br />\n你地和理非唔勇武係軟弱的表現<br />\n民意係完全無用的<br />\n民意一早歸佐邊 點做都唔會令人反對我地<br />\n<br />\nPS 依一類係將 對方的路線最為注重的事項 踢在腳底 完全否定 同 沒有邏輯思考發出最激的建議但完全無做到立論同解釋支持自己個論點 引起和理非手足極其不滿的方法<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n三毛和理非類<br />\n將勇武所有行動同民意綁架 (完全唔合理情況下)<br />\n勇武下次可唔可以唔好再做OXY 會比人入<br />\n你衝完政府都唔會理你 衝來無意思<br />\n依家應該由和理非接手 勇武先退場 (但無實際計劃 只係9UP)<br />\n你咁樣只係送頭<br />\n你咁做就好明顯係鬼 我會割蓆<br />\n批評勇武手足破壞運動<br />\n<br />\nPS 依一類係將 對方的路線行為 完全否定 否定勇武手足智商 用獨人階醉獨我醒的方法批評 同樣會做成勇武手足極其不滿的手法<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n重有好多我就唔詳細打啦 總知就係不斷開POST 用雙方最偏向自己路線的方法 去破壞個運動平衡 即係和理非同勇武互補的情況 從而引起雙方對大家的不滿<br />\n<br />\n我比的建議就係請大家討論個時應該語氣要好D 唔好一來就否定唔同立場手足的路線<br />\n對個建議有意見 講完就算 大家傾唔埋個時就各有各做 要記得我地係無大台 無人可以迫其他人做自己想做的事<br />\n不過如果個行動係引起好多的手足反對的話 都希望個位手足再三思一下點解會咁多人反對 而唔係發悔氣形式係到開POST屌鬼 引起新一輪的分化<br />\n我相信每次手足都有足夠的智慧去處理唔同的立場提出的意見<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n絶對認同<br />\n之前開嗰位巴打（香港沒有香港味 ）冇分台， 我幫佢分台等多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"e42aad2c135b952a1b5e73f05649b143a401babb","tid":1659013,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1e43ea42ecfba6543aa6c8d1697a8897de0162a3","tid":1659013,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:47:36.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警告!!!<br />\n連登已經被狗同三毛<br />\n嚴重滲透<br />\n加上仲有分化撚<br />\n熱門一片凌亂<br />\n再咁落去唔洗林奠出手<br />\n禁我地網 封鎖連登<br />\n連登就會從內部潰散<br />\n唯有預設不推文回覆<br />\n先可以光復連登</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議所有回覆預設係不推文回覆</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658904</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"43071b1a8e67070699467b9ddc0ef5c459df8414","tid":1659013,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"幫你推，始終依家多咗好多不同年齡層嘅香港人上連登<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1020 尖嘴見</span></span>"},{"pid":"5e58e249f36f04577b4029cb0b6ab37e90489ec8","tid":1659013,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"唔想再上連登 成班on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c57c7ea9a8fc714b449bb5c7be0693e09c7d9a","tid":1659013,"uid":181535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:56:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21f30566735b4e3f067bd4d9162ed33c2cd15ae0","tid":1659013,"uid":230759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"幫你推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d00de74d3b98409133c502d35b50cfb6c27ab6b","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be76c2c20d626fceb5e5a3f120f5ca7f211aadc4","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32f1c53bdd79f0000c1b7f01194a2fff3256f499","tid":1659013,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:13:22.000Z","msg":"之前立場嗰位勇武講過<br />\n佢哋成班好少留言<br />\n所以我信最激嗰班係偽勇武<br />\n目的係屌走和理非<br />\n所以無論如何都唔會同真勇武割"},{"pid":"29d38bf13e5166a0242426c422c5bdfc07df3156","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b41a38e71b1851cef4e43d96836067b59a06a2d","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf91e9b695c8f0ba9005bc1c79708fc914a463ac","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39aca0b59338faaf55e47a62d3773efa2bb1208c","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3926259779fbb4251a41e59b5daa1637ed64efc","tid":1659013,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n之前都講過"},{"pid":"cc7beea2af8c1143f6e7a2edf2395a9a7b242672","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1ae81a8cf3cf5b5c572a2ce48ef145cfdb3f1ac","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4079d7826122c363056e62f94de02fd96050c034","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:04:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"386e1668c071929da9b8f4062b6196e5a5a9c68a","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97003bb3e2308238763d3ef7a3daaea3d15517d0","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:11:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a464be915c531230596a2880d66f80f06c2f7e6e","tid":1659013,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:13:43.000Z","msg":"以前焦土都係咁玩"},{"pid":"b3d78e173d012916075be81bcbf77382875312bd","tid":1659013,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"呢兩日好嚴重"},{"pid":"a4526c6b524a432d7cf316fe4281f6f16245f8e3","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a732982f1875e2a2e2084763563998ecb9477d3a","tid":1659013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cc8c929fa78e7826e5d2232b492742516ebb58c","tid":1659013,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日出左個鬼文宣 今日引左